dct_description_sm: Survey of India. Alternate title: Eight inch Simla guide map, third edition. Insets: Mashobra (on the same scale), Continuation of Kasumpti (on the same scale), Jutogh (on the same scale), Simla neighborhod (1:253,440). Relief shown by 100 feet contour interval and spot heights.
